  "What is an accretion disk?": "",
  "A disk-shaped galaxy": "",
  "A planet's ring system": "",
  "A rotating disk of material spiraling onto a central object": "",
  "A type of star cluster": "",
  "Accretion disks form around protostars (and other objects) as infalling material conserves angular momentum.": "",
  "What is a Herbig-Haro object?": "",
  "A bright patch of nebulosity associated with jets from a young star": "",
  "A small rocky or metallic body orbiting the Sun within the inner solar system, left over from the era of planetary formation": "",
